            "id": 6008392,
            "title": "巨有科技攜華銀 啟動員工持股信託 強化攬才留才",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>ASIC 公司巨有科技 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWG:8227:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8227\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8227-TW</a>) 為提高員工福利、吸引及留任優秀人才，並凝聚員工向心力、提升經營績效，累積員工退休資產，與華南銀行攜手啟動員工持股信託，以實踐企業永續經營與人才永續發展的雙贏目標。 </p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008392%2Fl%2Fa4ab6b217d5989f37c4e138202523997.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008392%2Fl%2Fa4ab6b217d5989f37c4e138202523997.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008392%2Fl%2Fa4ab6b217d5989f37c4e138202523997.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008392%2Fl%2Fa4ab6b217d5989f37c4e138202523997.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008392%2Fl%2Fa4ab6b217d5989f37c4e138202523997.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008392%2Fl%2Fa4ab6b217d5989f37c4e138202523997.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008392%2Fl%2Fa4ab6b217d5989f37c4e138202523997.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008392%2Fl%2Fa4ab6b217d5989f37c4e138202523997.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008392%2Fl%2Fa4ab6b217d5989f37c4e138202523997.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008392%2Fl%2Fa4ab6b217d5989f37c4e138202523997.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008392%2Fl%2Fa4ab6b217d5989f37c4e138202523997.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008392%2Fl%2Fa4ab6b217d5989f37c4e138202523997.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008392%2Fl%2Fa4ab6b217d5989f37c4e138202523997.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008392%2Fl%2Fa4ab6b217d5989f37c4e138202523997.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008392%2Fl%2Fa4ab6b217d5989f37c4e138202523997.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008392%2Fl%2Fa4ab6b217d5989f37c4e138202523997.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008392%2Fl%2Fa4ab6b217d5989f37c4e138202523997.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">巨有董事長賴志賢。(鉅亨網資料照)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>巨有科技成立於 1991 年，為台積電設計中心聯盟 (Design Center Alliance, DCA) 成員，專注於 ASIC Turnkey 一站式服務、CyberShuttle 服務，提供 IP 授權服務、APR 設計服務、完整的 SoC 與 ASIC 設計與量產服務。每年完成超過 70 個專案，累計已達 1,000 個以上的設計定案 (Tape-out)，致力於為客戶提供更具成本效益的解決方案。 </p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>巨有科技深知在半導體產業的高度技術密集與人才競爭環境下，唯有從職涯規劃、職場環境、員工福利與員工參與等多面向著手，方能打造穩定且具吸引力的職場文化。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>巨有科技在今年開始啟動「員工持股信託」計畫，透過華南銀行提供的信託機制，並藉由公司優渥的 100% 提撥比率，讓員工以定期定額的方式購買公司股票，共享公司股東價值的穩健收益成果，同時也增加員工向心力，提升員工退休後生活品質，並為公司吸引及留任優秀人才，進一步提高企業競爭力。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
